e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uUPoVUWdr1g</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\nS20+ = Note 10+<br />\nS20  &gt; iPhone 11<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6pfN1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6pfN1c.jpg&h=b10c76a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xTWUkQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xTWUkQ.jpg&h=68e0577c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOne Ui 2.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNyMrg5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNyMrg5.gif&h=672f32c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQCeLyP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQCeLyP.gif&h=11031d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WxjJcA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WxjJcA.gif&h=9b51556d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGalaxy S20 建議：<br />\n120Hz+App Booster+封鎖白卡<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Labs集成系統優化。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">App Booster 提升App性能15%+5% 必裝！</span><br />\n(需直接裝2個apk 因香港未推）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sammobile.com%2Fnews%2Fsamsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=13d555ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n側邊手勢操作<br />\none hand operation<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.samsung.android.sidegesturepad&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=ca1963be\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad</a><br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾（勁有用）<br />\n<br />\n利用國防級的 Samsung Knox 安全平台，在您的三星手機上<span class=\"red\">打造一個私人的加密空間</span>。移至安全資料夾的<span class=\"red\">應用程序和數據</span>在設備中處於隔離的沙箱中，更可通過公共網絡安全瀏覽的Secure Wi-Fi以及可在設備被盜時遠程屏蔽的Find My Mobile等。其最新的Galaxy S20部件配備了安全芯片S3K250AF，。<br />\n<br />\n※ 設備中打造一個獨立的隔離環境。移動或添加至安全文件夾的應用程序和數據 (例如照片、音頻文件、電影文件和文檔) 將無法從安全文件夾外部訪問，無論是 USB 還是 Wi-Fi 直連都不可以。如果您的移動設備檢測到任何Root 權限獲取或ROM 自定義操作，為防止未授權的訪問，安全文件夾將自動鎖定，這種情況下，您將無法再訪問或使用安全文件夾中的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾操作邏輯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdVPvSOleYxU&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=ffe1518c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\nSmart Octopus<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCAHotc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCAHotc.gif&h=0cd5fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後360走了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWDVFJq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWDVFJq.png&h=9d1f42a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指紋錄入竅門<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=woTSMD0FAFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwoTSMD0FAFk&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=92f503de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=woTSMD0FAFk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n跟足呢兩條片Set 指紋真係秒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文字版:<br />\n1)左右拇指喺同一個指紋profile度交替咁錄<br />\n2)再重覆錄多個profile<br />\n3)喺Optimize battery 優化電池使用量閂咗com.samsung.android.biometric<br />\n唔怕裸機就搣埋張mon貼<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n常見問題<br />\n<br />\n1.呢家出S10/Note 10系列好唔好？<br />\n都係睇價，S/N10超過4000就加千幾上S20啦<br />\n<br />\n用完2代機，S20靠120hz體驗上係完完全全秒10系列。<br />\n<br />\n2. Google App 好食電？<br />\n裝置維護&gt;電量&gt;電量管理&gt;深度休眠&gt;加入Google<br />\n<br />\n2. 咩mon貼好，有埋人痴埋<br />\n<br />\nHoda 3D防爆9H玻璃貼(UV膠全貼合滿版）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n已改名抗藍義士<br />\n強烈建議admin永久封鎖會員 任何淫#255744 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958035\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958035</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b342e770eec451aa4e226d742ab064bfc0cf17ba","tid":2168860,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c92c9ba9940b9906b32ffa5f4f7bbee9e28fbcb","tid":2168860,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"【氣密檢測】三星手機 如何自己測試防水功能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面我來說一下怎麼測試自己的三星手機是否還具有密閉性！<br />\n<br />\n 一，首先打開撥號鍵盤，輸入&ldquo; <strong><span class=\"red\">*#0*#</span></strong> &rdquo;，進入之後點擊第三行中間的 sensor（傳感器）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/od5i9A6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fod5i9A6.jpg&h=f803322a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二，<strong><span class=\"red\">找到Barometer Sensor，這個就是氣壓計</span></strong>，下面顯示的就是相關的數據，而第一行以&ldquo;hPa&rdquo;為單位的就是手機的氣密性（第二個是海拔）。 <strong><span class=\"red\">此時用拇指按壓手機屏幕，觀察這個數值。 如果數值有明顯變化的話（大概是3-10左右，鬆開手指數值會恢復），那就代表氣密性良好，手機防水性能完好。 但是如果數值不變或者劇增劇減的話，那就代表氣密性已經受損，防水性能不如之前，此時手機會有進水的可能，謹慎下水。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjnBbPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjnBbPQ.jpg&h=2bbe8e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://m.samsungmembers.cn/thread-639461-4-10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.samsungmembers.cn%2Fthread-639461-4-10.html&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=7d01531c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.samsungmembers.cn/thread-639461-4-10.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7843f5dcd805ea122f96ff120ede2dfa4c7599d","tid":2168860,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64627f9e368709caa4fdbcc7b3d349774d5226a9","tid":2168860,"uid":187999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"有機未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家到手係咪會照裝app booster<br />\n同埋one hand operation"},{"pid":"66fcd68081949bf7eac16a86c2ec1167043d0c3c","tid":2168860,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"有PR出面post唱淡喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ba664a530e20fe22bdf7b4b9fa3d74252de32f","tid":2168860,"uid":679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"buds+買耳棉既話邊隻塞落個盒冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51351a71fa652b9227813d17917faf58cde1cee","tid":2168860,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:37:16.000Z","msg":"大家去返呢個post <br />\n我開多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamsung Galaxy 集中討論區 (91) Z Fold2 |Buds Live | Note20 倒數4日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2168345\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2168345</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}